Product Name: Fiamma F45 Zip Awning for Motorhomes & Campervans
Product Description:
Fiamma F45 Zip Motorhome, Caravan and Campervan Wind Out Awning

This Product is the Awning/Canopy only if you require the privacy room ZIP please add it here.

The Fiamma F45 Zip Awning is a special zipped version of the Fiamma F45 wind-out cassette awning that is designed for caravan, campervans and motorhomes. It features zips on the edge of the canopy roof fabric that allow you to attach the Fiamma ZIP Privacy Room (sold separately) to turn the awning into a complete, enclosed living space.

The Fiamma ZIP Awning is available in lengths from 300 to 450 centimeters to suit a range of vehicle sizes. It comes with a standard installation kit for mounting to the wall of coachbuilt motorhomes. Optional fitting kits are available for non-standard installation and to fit to other flat wall vans.

Features:

  • Easy to install and set up
  • Water and wind resistant
  • Provides total privacy
  • Doubles your motorhome living space
  • Creates a fully enclosed room (sometimes referred to as a Safari Room)

Compatibility:

The Fiamma ZIP Awning is only compatible with the Fiamma ZIP Privacy Room. It cannot be used with standard privacy rooms or with standard Fiamma F45S awnings.

Suitability:

The Fiamma ZIP Awning is suitable for motorhomes with a mounting height of between 225 and 280 centimeters from the ground.

Order your Fiamma F45 Zip Awning today and experience the fastest and easiest way to create a spacious and comfortable living space for your motorhome!

Note:

The Fiamma Zip Privacy Room is not included with the Fiamma ZIP Awning. It must be purchased separately.

Note to customers in Northern Ireland - unfortunately due to shipping costs we cannot fulfil any orders to Northern Ireland. Any orders placed will be refunded.

Any returns that you have ordered incorrectly are subject to a restocking charge. For advice please call before ordering 0151 334 0222

Product Description:
Fiamma F35 Pro Caravan and Camper Van Awning

Ultralight caravan and Camper Van awning

The sleek Fiamma F35 Pro Caravan and Campervan Awning provides a strong yet incredibly lightweight canopy. Encased within a protective aluminium case, this awning is robust without being overly heavy. The Fiamma F35 Pro Caravan & Camper Van Awning can be fixed to any kind of minivan, caravan or campervan thanks to a variety of dedicated Fiamma brackets and awning installation kits available separately.

Easy to pitch, easy to use

The F35 Pro Caravan and Camper Van awning keeps things simple and straight forward, helping to minimise pitching time. Using integrated telescopic legs folding out from the awning roller tube and reinforced tensioning arms, the awning fabric stays taut and sag free.

Flexible installation options

Using one of the separate Fiamma mounting adapters, the F35 Pro Caravan and Campervan Awning can be attached as a wall or roof mounted installation, suitable for a wide range of caravan, motorhome or campervan vehicles.

Available in a range of colours

The Fiamma F35 Pro awning fabric is available in either Royal Grey or Royal Blue, with a choice of the Titanium or Black cassette to compliment the finish to your caravan, motorhome or campervan.

Fiamma F35 Pro Caravan & Campervan Awning Features:

  • Telescopic leg and arm supports in anodised aluminium
  • Aluminium roller tube stores legs and arms when rolled away
  • Compact awning cassette reduces wind noise during transit
  • Compact awning cassette
  • Quick to set up and pitch once installed

Canopy Fabric Features:

  • Multi-layered robust, washable and flame retardant fabric construction
  • Double sided design with light reflective properties to keep the canopy if the weathers hot
  • Resistant to UV fading sunlight
  • Rot Proof to accommodate for wet conditions

Product Description:
Fiamma F45L Caravan and Motorhome Large Awning

Ideal for larger motorhomes and caravans thanks to the strong box and extra large roller tube, the Fiamma F45L Large Awning is suitable for many commercial and leisure related applications and features the latest updated redesign to be the most advanced and functional F45L awning to date.

User friendly and quiet to open and close, the Fiamma F45L Caravan and Motorhome Large Awning provides the largest possible shaded area and features a case made from extra strong extruded aluminium making it incredibly lightweight and resistant to the elements.

Fiamma F45L Caravan & Motorhome Large Awning features

  • Easy and safe to operate
  • Large canopy surface providing maximum shade
  • Fitted regulation system for the smooth closure of the front lead bar
  • Secure Auto-Lock
  • Dual Security system to indicate the correct closure of the front bar 

Fiamma F45L Caravan & Motorhome Large Awning comes supplied with:

  • Presto Fix
  • Reinforced arms with twin cable
  • Extra Strong Arms
  • Dual Shock Absorber
  • Auto-Lock
  • Dual Security
  • Telescopic Crank Handle
  • AS Brackets and internal 'M' bracket covers
  • Hooks to secure legs to the ground
  • Wall brackets for leg support to the motorhome
  • Tension Rafter (2 pieces with F45 L 550).

Product Description:
Thetford Fridge N4080 Caravan Motorhome 3 Way Wheel Arch Model (Replaces N3080)

The Thetford N4080E Caravan and Motorhome Fridge is a quiet running and compact 3 way, absorption refrigerator making it ideal for campervans, motorhomes or caravans with a limited amount of space to spare!

A lockable door means that the Thetford N4080E Caravan and Motorhome fridge will stay securely shut whilst your vehicle is in transit, while adjustable door bins, shelving and a bottle slide will keep your goods from moving about or coming loose within the fridge.

A powerful, high performing compact caravan fridge, the Thetford N4080E has an ample capacity of 81 litres (inclusive of the freezer compartment) making it ideal for essentials and little luxuries - and it also features electric ignition.

Please note: The Thetford N4080E Caravan and Motorhome Fridge is now supplied with a reversible hinge as standard and as such can be installed as either a left or right handed hinge. The Thetford N4080E replaces the N3080 and N80 Fridges.

Product Name: Fiamma F45 Eagle Motorhome Automatic Electric Awning
Product Description:
Fiamma F45 Eagle Caravan and Motorhome Automatic Electric Awning

An ultra-strong 12Vcc automatic legless awning designed for roof installation

Combining an innovative design with convenience and outstanding strength, the Fiamma F45 Eagle Caravan and Motorhome Automatic Electric Awning is a legs free 12Vcc awning system which can be easily opened by a switch inserted in the wall of the vehicle.  

The Fiamma F45 Eagle Caravan and Motorhome Automatic Electric Awning features the Wind Detective® system which automatically activates the 12Vcc motor and closes the awning when strong winds are detected by the wind sensor providing a safe prevention of any potential damages.

The sturdy and innovative duralumin Double Block® doesn’t require the use of support legs and provides robust reinforcement to the telescopic self-supporting arms.

Fiamma F45 Eagle Caravan and Motorhome Automatic Electric Awning features

  • Wall control for easy automatic electric opening and closing of the awning
  • Wind Detective® System for wind damage prevention
  • Motor kit allows for manual closing in case of emergency
  • Safe to operate
  • Supplied with sturdy all aluminium brackets, spacers and internal counterbacks for a safe and solid installation

Please note: The arms of the Fiamma F45 Eagle Automatic Awning are at a prefixed angle of inclination of 10 degrees, however can be adjusted from 5 to 17 degrees to suit the height requirements of your caravan or motorhome and to enable for the correct flow of water.

Installation brackets are available separately.

Any returns that you have ordered incorrectly are subject to a restocking charge. For advice please call before ordering 0151 334 0222

Product Description:
Fiamma F65 Eagle Caravan & Motorhome Automatic Electric Awning

For the most comfortable, convenient and robust caravan and motorhome awning yet, the Fiamma F65 Eagle is a legs free 12Vcc automatic awning system which can be easily controlled via a simple switch inserted in the wall of the vehicle.

Product Description:
Whale Premium and Hi-Flow Submersible Pumps

Receive high quality and reliably superb flow performances with the Whale Premium and Hi-Flow Submersible Pumps.

With their long lifespan, quiet operations and low power consumption the Whale Premium and Hi-Flow Submersible Pumps are incredibly durable and built for endurance.

Premium or Hi-Flow?

The Whale Premium Submersible Pump provides 13 litres per minute and as well as being suitable for general purpose and suitable for multiple outlets the Whale Premium Submersible Pump is also an inexpensive and easy way to update a manual to an electric system. The Hi-Flow Submersible Pump, on the other hand, provides a powerful flow rate of 16 litres per minute making it suitable for applications such as showering.

To get the most out of your Whale Premium and Hi-Flow Submersible Pumps

  • Don’t exceed the maximum continuous operation time of 15 minutes
  • Don’t run the Whale Premium or Hi-Flow Submersible Pump dry or in water over 60oc as this can cause damage
  • We recommend standing the Whale Premium and Hi-Flow Submersible Pumps vertically in the tank
  • Before switching the submersible pump on, place it in water and shake for a few seconds to release any trapped air to ensure for successful priming. Repeat after refilling in the water tank
  • To boost water flow, why not add an in-line pump to your system too?

Product Description:
Sargent Universal Control Panel for Power Management Systems

Replacement Panel for EC328 EC325 EC225 and EC200 in Motorhomes and Caravans

This replacement Universal Control panel is compatible with the Sargent EC328 power supply unit that is designed for use in motorhomes, caravans and campervans, the Sargent Universal Control Panel is a new, universal version of the digital control panel.

This Universal Control Panel has an extensive list of features (all of which are fully covered in the Sargent EC328 Control Panel Manual) including an auto battery protect circuit, clock alarm with event timer*, scrolling menu system which displays system information including water levels, battery voltage and electrical current* (the control panel connects to the PSU via a 20 way data cable which is available separately). An optional external temperature probe can also be connected to the panel (not included).

* indicates features dependent on the type of PSU being used.

Compatibility 

This Universal control panel is suitable for the EC328, EC325, EC225 and EC200. Depending on which 12v/240v Sargent Power Control system you are using on your Campervan, Caravan or Motorhome, the Sargent Universal Control Panel options can be selected on install in the settings when the panel is turned off.

Product Name: Dometic-Cramer HSG 2445 (Cramer CE00-MINI/BO-HI/27-I-G) Hob & Sink Combination Unit
Product Description:
Dometic HSG 2445 2 Burner Hob & Sink Combination Unit

A space efficient and convenient sink and hob combination unit by Dometic

The Dometic HSG 2445 2 burner hob & sink combination Unit is a space efficient hob and sink combination unit for caravans, motor homes, campervans and boats. 

Making the most of small spaces

For full maximisation of space the Dometic 2 burner hob & sink combination unit features a heat resistant safety glass lid (which can also double up as a work surface when the Dometic sink and hob aren’t in use) whilst enamelled pan supports can be easily detached from the Dometic 2 burner hob & sink combination unit for easily cleaning.

Flame Failure Device

A flame failure device is included for peace of mind that the gas will shut off if the flame is extinguished unexpectedly. 

The HSG 2445 hob and sink combi can be supplied with the Arona chrome cold or mixer tap from the option set above.

Dometic Hob & Sink Combination Unit Features include:

  • Enamelled burner caps
  • Flame-failure device
  • Rubber seal and siphon included
  • Heat resistant glass lid
  • This model has no 12v Ignition
  • Detachable enamelled pan supports for easy cleaning
  • This unit has a 27mm tap hole
  • Please note, the Arona tap is only suitable for pressures of up to 1.5 bar (21psi)
  • Approx. sink dimensions 310mm at widest point, 300mm mid point and 200 at narrowest point (front) 95mm deep. Front to back is 280mm

Product Description:
Dometic Cool-Ice WCI-22 Coolbox

The Dometic Cool-ice WCI22 cool box is designed to keep ice for anything up to 10 days depending on model usage and conditions that it’s used in. Popular for weekend getaways and camping trips and robust enough to deal with the continuous exposure to weather experienced on boats, the WCI22 is a robust all rounder.

With impact resistant, seamless rotomoulded plastic this Dometic coolbox boasts "indestructible" durability with a unique labyrinth seal design to ensure superior ice storage. With food grade polyethylene construction and refrigeration grade foam insulation the Dometic WCI 22 is hygienic and easy to clean with A+++ efficiency rating.

Dometic Cool Ice WCI-22 Key Features:-

  • Low heat absorption
  • Seamless casing
  • Highly durable for the toughest conditions
  • 5 year guarantee!
  • Melt water drain plug
  • Steel Pin Hinges
  • ABS Clasps for easy lock and seal
  • Large none slip feet
  • Keeps ice frozen for several days
  • Food grade polyethylene CFC free material
  • Durable, hygienic and easy to clean
  • A+++ efficiency rating
  • Handy shoulder strap

 

Best Usage;

 

  • Chill all groceries and drinks before use and pack the boxes as full as possible(standard freezer packs or ice cubes are suitable as coolants).
  • Store the ice box in a cool area for several hours before and during use, making sure to keep it out of direct sunlight.
  • Please avoid opening the coolbox unnecessarily as air will compromise the cooling capacity and limit the cooling duration.
  • Ambient temperatures still play a part in the capacity to keep ice for longer so please be aware that the maximum time given for keeping ice can vary due to this.
Product Availability: The WCI22 is currently out of stock.

Product Description:
Swimming Pool Solar Heating Pod

Compatible for use with either in ground or above ground pools, our Swimming Pool Solar Pods are a space, eco and energy efficient method for providing expandable heating to your swimming pool.

Every watt of swimming pool solar heating is sourced from the suns natural energy, making this free source of energy an exceptionally cost effective addition to an existing heating system. Featuring a strong transparent polycarbonate dome that reduces heat loss from the wind, these Swimming Pool Solar Pods retain heat incredibly well and can also be tilted in order to harness the best angle for sunshine.

Incredibly low maintenance, Solar Heating Pods require no servicing apart from Winterising, and also benefit from being superbly easy to install, simply requiring a Philips screwdriver and silicon lubricant to carry out the installation. Set them up on a roof in close proximity to the pool, or even next to the pool itself; at only 580 x 580mm, Swimming Pool Solar Pods take up very little space, and as such are ideal for when you don’t have a lot of room to spare! 

 

Each pod is designed to heat 4500 litres but can be easily scaled up for larger pools with additional pods. We recommend that customers phone for advice on solar pods, as there’s quite a few considerations to bear in mind regarding the quantity of solar pods required for your specific pool size as well as positioning of the solar pods (i.e. installation on roofs or in positions away from the filtration system can require more powerful pumps). Tel 0151 334 0222.

The Eco Swimming Pool Solar Heating Pod Kit includes:

Main Base With Stand
1.25"-1.5" hose Reducer
Collared Tube Adaptor
Hose Clamps
Thick Connector Gasket
1m Hose
Side Hose Connector (x2)
380mm Hose
Clear Dome
Solar Protection Cover

Note: For use with Intex standard filtration you will need to purchase 1.25" hose

Product Name: Dometic Seitz S4 Hinged Caravan and Motorhome Windows
Product Description:
Dometic Seitz S4 Hinged Windows

The secure, hinged window system with roller blind, fly net and safety catch

An ideal complete window system for caravans, motorhomes and horsebox and van conversions, the Dometic Seitz S4 hinged window is incredibly quick and easy to install and comes with a set of features for added user friendliness. As well as being fabulously energy efficient thanks to its thermal insulation, the Dometic Seitz S4 hinged window also benefits from an integrated roller blind and fly net which offer ease of movement and control against the elements! The Dometic Seitz S4 hinged window also provides a safety catch for added security to prevent it from being opened from the outside.

 Dometic Seitz S4 hinged window additional features

  • A simple, fast installation to wall thickness from 26mm to 41mm by trimming the interior frame.
  • Outer and inner frames of the Seitz S4 hinged window are screwed together from the inside which then clamps the window to the vehicle wall (applying pressure for a robust, reliable seal)
  • The Dometic Seitz S4 hinged window features a black outer frame, cream inner frame and a white interior with aluminium coating to the outside.

Certain unusual sizes might occasionally be out of stock, in which case we can arrange for them to be drop-shipped directly to you. Typically, this process takes around 7 days, though delays have been more frequent this year due to ongoing issues with Dometic. We’ll keep you informed if this affects your order.

Product Name: Dometic Seitz Mini Heki Style Caravan & Motorhome Roof Light Vent
Product Description:
Dometic Seitz Mini Heki Style Campervan Caravan & Motorhome Roof light

Featuring an easily adjustable fly net and blind for ultimate shading and pest control, the Dometic Seitz Heki Style roof light provides great thermal insulation and protection from the elements thanks to its proven Duette Honeycomb system.

To Ventilate or Not: Choosing the Right Option

Fixed Ventilation:

Offers continuous airflow even when closed, making it perfect for caravans to prevent condensation buildup. However, it may lead to wind noise and whistling when installed in campervans or motorhomes.

Without Fixed Ventilation:

Provides a complete seal when closed, ideal for campervans and motorhomes seeking noise reduction during travel.

Dometic Seitz Midi Heki Caravan Campervan & Motorhome Roof Light

Roof window with Blind and Fly Screen

The Dometic Seitz Dometic Midi Heki is big on style and big on ventilation! Equipped to open in 3 different positions (wide, half and a position for bad weather, which reliably keeps rain from splashing through), this campervan caravan and motorhome roof window with double glazed panes has a robust, reliable build and comes ready for installation. Dometic’s Midi Heki roof light is designed with an inner frame and separately adjustable blind and fly screen to keep sunlight and insects out. The frame is made of durable, weather-resistant plastic, making the Midi Heki Skylight suitable for harsh weather conditions. 

Aerodynamically shaped roof light

Featuring a durable, weatherproof frame and an aerodynamically shaped, light grey tinted acrylic dome (which automatically locks when closed), the Dometic Seitz Midi Heki Caravan & Motorhome Roof Light also has a die cast finish to prevent unwanted frequencies of light from getting through and is set up for easy cleaning.

The Dometic Midi Heki includes an installation kit for a roof thickness of 30mm to 33mm, for roof thicknesses less or more than this size you will require an extra kit, just click here.

Product Name: Zodiac Baracuda Super G Swimming Pool Cleaner
Product Description:
Baracuda Super G+ Swimming Pool Suction Cleaner

Quite possibly the greatest swimming pool cleaner in the World, the Baracuda Super G+ Swimming Pool Suction Cleaner is a versatile, innovative model that not only delivers a first class cleaning performance but will also protect your swimming pool pump from wayward debris.

Using the exclusive ‘Baracuda Diaphragm’ technology, the Baracuda Super G+ Swimming Pool Suction Cleaner is designed to deliver high performance cleaning for all in-ground pools via connection to the pool skimmer or suction line with the power from the pool’s pump enabling it to automatically move around your pool and suck up debris at random.

Thanks to its open double disk, the Baracuda Super G+ Swimming Pool Suction Cleaner is engineered to avoid obstacles, climb and clean the walls as well as the floor and for optimum cleaning efficiency is also equipped with a leaf trap to collect debris before it gets the chance to reach your pump basket.

Please note: The Baracuda Super G+ has now been discontinued. For suitable alternatives, please look at the Baracuda MX8 Suction Cleaner or the Baracuda B3 Suction Cleaner.

Baracuda Super G+ Swimming Pool Suction Cleaner Features:

  • Resistant two tone hose
  • 12 hose section of 1 metre lengths
  • Flow tester
  • Automatic flow adjustment valve
  • High suction power
  • Leaf trap
  • 3 year warranty

 Please Note: Requires a minimum of 3/4 HP pump for correct operation.
